  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of using 2h-UG combined with FPG, AGEsP alone or in combination with FPG in
      diabetes screening in Chinese natural population
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Using the WHO criteria as the golden standard，drawing the ROC curve of 2h-UG combined with
      FPG, AGEsP alone or in combination with FPG，calculating the area under the ROC curve.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
